Dependencies:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Apache >= 2.0
  Modules: htaccess, mod_headers, mod_expires, mod_rewrite, mod_deflate, mod_php5, mod_mime

* PHP >= 5.3
  Modules: apache2 bcmath calendar curl curlwrappers gd inifile mysql snmp soap sockets sqlite3 sysvipc xmlreader xmlrpc xmlwriter xsl zip pdo imap mhash postgres tidy wddx mysqli intl pcntl gettext

* MySQL >= 5.0
  Modules. UTF-8

* 'msgfmt'
  Included in Linux

* 'exiftool'
  Debian users: apt-get install exiftool
  Gentoo users: emerge exiftool
  Download: http://www.sno.phy.queensu.ca/~phil/exiftool/

* 'pdf2svg'
  Debian users: apt-get install pdf2svg
  Gentoo users: emerge pdf2svg
  Download: http://www.cityinthesky.co.uk/opensource/pdf2svg

* 'jsl' (JSLint)
  Debian users must do: apt-get install python{X}.{Y}-dev (python --version)
  Download: svn co https://javascriptlint.svn.sourceforge.net/svnroot/javascriptlint/trunk jsl

Apache:
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Use example from doc/XX_apache-vhost.conf
* Create /var/cache/OSjs with permission to apache

Deployment (Development Target):
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Clone the project from GitHub
* Fix (temporary) permissions with './bin/fix-permissions dev'
> See "Deployment (All Targets)"
* Create documentation wit './bin/documentation-gen'
* Fix permissions with './bin/fix-permissions live'

Deployment (Production Target):
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Clone the project from GitHub
* Fix (temporary) permissions with './bin/fix-permissions dev'
> See "Deployment (All Targets)"
* Compress/Minimize all resources with './bin/minimize-all'
* Fix permissions with './bin/fix-permissions live'

Deployment (All Targets):
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Compile server-side locales. wit './bin/makelocale.sh'
* Use a vhost template in 'doc/' and implement into Apache configuration
* Update "php.ini" for the host or enable runtime ini_set for project.
  The settings are found in the top of 'header.php'
* Copy a X11's icon theme 16x16 and 32x32 folders into 'public_html/img/icons/'
* Clone the "OSjs-Packages" repository into 'src/packages'
  * Compile all applications with './bin/application-gen'
  * Install all applications globally with './bin/install-all'

Upgrading (Production Target):
-------------------------------------------------------------------------------
* Run './bin/update'
